About Me

Education

  • BSc Oceanography (University of Vigo 2005-2010)

  • BSc Biology (University of Santiago de Compostela 2010-2012)

  • MSc Microbiology (University Complutense of Madrid 2013-2014)

  • PhD Oceanography (Institute of Marine Research - IIM-CSIC, Vigo 2015-2018)

You can find more information in the map. The little points in the ocean are stations of the oceanographic cruises in which I have participated so far: the “Reykjanes Ridge Experiment” (RREX) in 2015 and 2017; the “BOCATS-OVIDE” in 2016, 2018 and 2021 and the FICARAM cruise in 2019.
